{
  "article_id": "Hudson1980",
  "paragraphs": [
    [
      {
        "text": "IN TWO PREVIOUS ISSUES OF",
        "tropes": [
          4
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "THE MASTERKEY",
        "tropes": [
          4
        ],
        "entity_key": "masterkey",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "("
      },
      {
        "text": "Vol. 52, Nos. 1 & 4, 1978) several exciting discoveries of ethnographic notes pertaining to ",
        "tropes": [
          4
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the \"Lone Woman\" of San Nicolas Island",
        "tropes": [
          4
        ],
        "entity_key": "lw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "were reported.",
        "tropes": [
          4
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "These notes were found among the extensive papers of "
      },
      {
        "text": "John P. Harrington",
        "entity_key": "jha",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "for the "
      },
      {
        "text": "Ventureño Chumash",
        "entity_key": "natam_Ventureno",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": ". Recently, however, two additional notes on "
      },
      {
        "text": "the \"Lone Woman\"",
        "entity_key": "lw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "have surfaced among Harrington's papers for the "
      },
      {
        "text": "Barbareño Chumash",
        "entity_key": "natam_Barbareno",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": ". Interviewed in "
      },
      {
        "text": "Santa Barbara",
        "entity_key": "ci_sb",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "some time between 1912 and 1922, the informant in this case was "
      },
      {
        "text": "Luisa Ygnacio",
        "entity_key": "lyg",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ", a full-blood Barbareño Chumash who was baptized at "
      },
      {
        "text": "Mission Santa Barbara",
        "entity_key": "mi_santabarbaramission",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "about 1830. "
      },
      {
        "text": "Harrington",
        "entity_key": "jha",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "used the abbreviation[s] \"Sa.\" and \"La.\" when referring to her (Blackburn 1975: 19)."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "The first short note is as follows:"
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "\""
      },
      {
        "text": "Sa.",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "lyg",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "has never seen a shell fishhook, except the one that ",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the last woman of San Nicolas",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "lw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "had",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": ". It was a big shell fishhook, and [the] fishline [with it] was as thick as a lead pencil. "
      },
      {
        "text": "Sa.'s spouse",
        "entity_key": "poli",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "brought it.1 "
      },
      {
        "text": "Sa.",
        "entity_key": "lyg",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "had it at "
      },
      {
        "text": "Sa.'s home on the ranch",
        "entity_key": "sahome",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ", but after a while it got thrown away. "
      },
      {
        "text": "Sa.",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "lyg",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "also had at ",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the ranch",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "sahome",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "two feather capes belonging to ",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the last woman of San Nicolas",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "lw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "which ",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "Sa.'s spouse",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "poli",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "brought at the same time that he brought the fishhook.",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "2 These were small (not big) and were made by sewing together seagull skins with [the] feathers still on, "
      },
      {
        "text": "Sa.",
        "entity_key": "lyg",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "thinks. [The] feathers [were] on [the] outside [of the capes]. Used them [by wearing them] thrown over [the] shoulders. When "
      },
      {
        "text": "Sa.'s spouse",
        "entity_key": "poli",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "died, "
      },
      {
        "text": "Sa.",
        "entity_key": "lyg",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "threw the capes and hook away.3\""
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "The second note mentions these details concerning "
      },
      {
        "text": "the woman",
        "entity_key": "lw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ":"
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "\""
      },
      {
        "text": "They had ",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "the last woman of San Nicolas Island",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "lw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "here in ",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "Santa Barbara",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ],
        "entity_key": "ci_sb",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ".",
        "tropes": [
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "Sa.",
        "entity_key": "lyg",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "did not go to see her, but many people did. "
      },
      {
        "text": "Martina",
        "entity_key": "martina",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "went to see her, and either "
      },
      {
        "text": "Martina",
        "entity_key": "martina",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "or others said she talked like a "
      },
      {
        "text": "Fernandina",
        "entity_key": "natam_Fernandenos",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": ".4 So they got "
      },
      {
        "text": "Pilar",
        "entity_key": "pilar",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "to come and try to talk with her.5 "
      },
      {
        "text": "Pilar",
        "entity_key": "pilar",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "talked good Barbareño Chumash, but she never forgot her native tongue and talked it when the "
      },
      {
        "text": "Fernandinos",
        "entity_key": "natam_Fernandenos",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "came here to "
      },
      {
        "text": "Santa Barbara",
        "entity_key": "ci_sb",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ". "
      },
      {
        "text": "Pilar",
        "entity_key": "pilar",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "tried to talk with "
      },
      {
        "text": "the woman",
        "entity_key": "lw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "in Fernandina, but she said she could not understand.6"
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "\"If they had let "
      },
      {
        "text": "the woman",
        "entity_key": "lw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "stay with the Indians here, she would have been all right. But they kept her with "
      },
      {
        "text": "Qorqe",
        "entity_key": "gni",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "("
      },
      {
        "text": "George Nidever",
        "entity_key": "gni",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "). "
      },
      {
        "text": "Martina",
        "entity_key": "martina",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and "
      },
      {
        "text": "Pilar",
        "entity_key": "pilar",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "came from "
      },
      {
        "text": "Ventura",
        "entity_key": "ci_ven",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "one time and got some clams and maybe some other things on the road, and when they passed by here, in "
      },
      {
        "text": "Santa Barbara",
        "entity_key": "ci_sb",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ", they visited "
      },
      {
        "text": "the woman",
        "entity_key": "lw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and gave her the clams. "
      },
      {
        "text": "The woman",
        "entity_key": "lw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "was greatly pleased. "
      },
      {
        "text": "Martina",
        "entity_key": "martina",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and "
      },
      {
        "text": "Pilar",
        "entity_key": "pilar",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "had just made a little trip to "
      },
      {
        "text": "Ventura",
        "entity_key": "ci_ven",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ". "
      },
      {
        "text": "Sa.",
        "entity_key": "lyg",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "thinks they had seen "
      },
      {
        "text": "the woman",
        "entity_key": "lw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "before that time.\""
      }
    ],
